{"tid":420683,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《失蹤女神依然索》閃電傳真機張沅薇　尚品薈做知客","createTime":"2017-10-01T15:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T07:45:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2f27a465654c5a593491b696c76788a216ab56aa","tid":420683,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:22:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oFt4P7T-7eA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoFt4P7T-7eA&d=ANzux6gLU2iQwq5JWIuDgZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=eed801fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oFt4P7T-7eA</a><br />\n發佈日期：2016年12月23日<br />\n訂閱 19.2萬<br />\n SUBSCRIBE SUBSCRIBED UNSUBSCRIBE<br />\n咦咦！乜呢個知客咁省鏡嘅，成副明星相喎！人哋真係明星嚟㗎，九十後有睇過《閃電傳真機》嘅，一定記得，佢咪《殭屍爺孫》裏面殭屍爺爺個外孫女，真名叫張沅薇，當年係女神嚟。<br />\n<br />\n張沅薇model出身，拍過幾部電視劇，之後同音樂人王雙駿拍拖，仲生咗個仔。後來佢哋分開咗，佢一個人帶住個仔，自食其力。做過秘書又做過牆紙客戶服務推廣。佢話︰「轉咗行好耐，中間做咗秘書，間接識咗依家呢個老闆，佢叫我入嚟做，都係公關工作。」<br />\n<br />\n佢好敬業樂業，喺好多圈中人幫襯嘅新派粵菜館尚品薈做知客，見佢做到冇時停，真係要頒個勤工獎俾佢。"},{"pid":"44a2e9465a644c3ac91ba7eb7b450e7a90cbd264","tid":420683,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:24:47.000Z","msg":"細個見佢有個單元，著紫色衫，好窄覺得個胸好大同突點，唔知有冇記錯"},{"pid":"e792825e932555ab276a53f1b9257099c849c6c6","tid":420683,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a378a7dfbda9c79585d97326c7a302a153b52b22","tid":420683,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T19:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4ae7f5d3392fd529e3a954bb858325ef375fec","tid":420683,"uid":119330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T22:42:39.000Z","msg":"好心班仆街記者就唔好搞人啦<br />\n人地已經淡出左呢個圈<br />\n正正經經咁做野<br />\n都要比你班仆街拉返出黎<br />\n<br />\nBTW 條女真係幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98036364ed2274780f98b6d44ec6f0633c3e421","tid":420683,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:02:16.000Z","msg":"90後未必識喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢90年代初做閃電傳真機，93年就無做，之後拍過下戲，其實佢個演藝生涯都好短暫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deca6f57372402f7abad6db5f5a709f19edab73a","tid":420683,"uid":33756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:24:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>90後未必識喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢90年代初做閃電傳真機，93年就無做，之後拍過下戲，其實佢個演藝生涯都好短暫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吉野妹原來撚老架...夢想幻滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc3dd3a4d85abf50ba62a90606e184966a72c68","tid":420683,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>90後未必識喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢90年代初做閃電傳真機，93年就無做，之後拍過下戲，其實佢個演藝生涯都好短暫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吉野妹原來咁撚老架...夢想幻滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"131796d238e7f594f3bf5d9a62e9952f07eb9f22","tid":420683,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T02:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>90後未必識喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢90年代初做閃電傳真機，93年就無做，之後拍過下戲，其實佢個演藝生涯都好短暫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吉野妹原來咁撚老架...夢想幻滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n不嬲都話40路嚟喎，係你自己幻想咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60c847937130187f61a12e0102540cd13170e94","tid":420683,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislik